merge_windowsannotationdataONlinuxsystem¶

deeplabcut.utils.merge_windowsannotationdataONlinuxsystem(cfg)[source]¶

If a project was created on Windows (and labeled there,) but ran on unix then the data folders corresponding in the keys in cfg[‘video_sets’] are not found. This function gets them directly by looping over all folders in labeled-data
